325
00:17:46,680 --> 00:17:48,510
I like you, too!

326
00:17:48,670 --> 00:17:50,040
Me too!

327
00:17:57,350 --> 00:17:58,110
By the way,

328
00:17:58,280 --> 00:17:59,790
I've asked the Design Dept to

329
00:17:59,790 --> 00:18:00,630
