335
00:18:07,430 --> 00:18:08,520
You may go first.

336
00:18:09,270 --> 00:18:10,310
Don't drink too much.

337
00:18:30,440 --> 00:18:31,440
What are you looking at?

338
00:18:34,230 --> 00:18:35,110
Nothing.

339
00:18:38,430 --> 00:18:39,270
How is the partnership

340
00:18:39,840 --> 00:18:41,670
