343
00:18:56,560 --> 00:18:58,910
[Who would dare touch his woman?]

344
00:19:01,920 --> 00:19:04,110
What is making you so happy?

345
00:19:06,320 --> 00:19:07,800
The company's financial statements.

346
00:19:16,070 --> 00:19:17,440
Earlier on,

347
00:19:17,440 --> 00:19:18,920
I ran into Simon downstairs.

348
00:19:20,110 --> 00:19:21,390
He came back with me.

349
00:19:21,390 --> 00:19:22,720
He's busy so he left.

350
00:19:26,430 --> 00:19:27,190
By the way,

351
00:19:28,600 --> 00:19:30,440
Ms. Qin said that

352
00:19:31,150 --> 00:19:32,230
