353
00:19:32,560 --> 00:19:33,200
You were there as well.

354
00:19:36,560 --> 00:19:37,950
Why did you ask?

355
00:19:39,990 --> 00:19:41,440
Nothing, I'm curious.

356
00:19:44,430 --> 00:19:45,550
How should I put it?

357
00:19:46,350 --> 00:19:47,880
It's not like I was there

358
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:48,430
when they went on a blind date.

359
00:19:48,430 --> 00:19:49,430
To be precise,

360
00:19:49,430 --> 00:19:50,400
I was present

361
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:50,910
when Simon went on

362
00:19:51,190 --> 00:19:51,920
all of his blind dates.

363
00:19:52,630 --> 00:19:53,840
I was still young at that time.

364
00:19:53,840 --> 00:19:55,390
My dad was busy with his business.

365
00:19:55,390 --> 00:19:56,670
He left me with my uncle.

366
00:19:56,670 --> 00:19:57,600
But my uncle

367
00:19:57,600 --> 00:19:58,600
was not any older than me.

368
00:19:58,800 --> 00:19:59,990
He was busy with his company

369
00:19:59,990 --> 00:20:01,070
and he had to take care of me.

370
00:20:01,070 --> 00:20:02,160
He had no time to date

371
00:20:02,160 --> 00:20:03,840
so he had to go to these blind dates.

372
00:20:05,520 --> 00:20:06,750
If I hadn't helped him

373
00:20:06,750 --> 00:20:08,040
deal with those girls

374
00:20:08,040 --> 00:20:09,190
on his blind dates,

375
00:20:09,190 --> 00:20:09,590
Simon would have

376
00:20:09,590 --> 00:20:11,240
suffered a lot more.

377
00:20:14,360 --> 00:20:16,190
He really listens to you.

378
00:20:17,520 --> 00:20:18,600
How do I put it?

379
00:20:18,600 --> 00:20:19,200
Sometimes,

380
00:20:19,200 --> 00:20:20,280
only a woman

381
00:20:20,280 --> 00:20:21,670
can see a woman better.

382
00:20:21,670 --> 00:20:22,670
If I don't like the girl,

383
00:20:22,670 --> 00:20:23,990
Simon won't like her, either.

384
00:20:25,280 --> 00:20:26,270
What about you?

385
00:20:28,280 --> 00:20:29,590
Do you like him?

386
00:20:29,590 --> 00:20:31,070
Of course.

387
00:20:31,070 --> 00:20:32,440
I prefer the way Simon looks after me

388
00:20:32,440 --> 00:20:33,630
than that of my dad.

389
00:20:33,630 --> 00:20:34,120
Back then,

390
00:20:34,120 --> 00:20:35,430
