391
00:20:41,350 --> 00:20:42,630
I think...

392
00:20:45,950 --> 00:20:46,830
What's the matter?

393
00:20:47,960 --> 00:20:48,710
I think we've lived here

394
00:20:48,710 --> 00:20:50,080
long enough.

395
00:20:50,480 --> 00:20:52,110
Let's move back to the apartment tomorrow.

396
00:20:52,270 --> 00:20:53,550
It's kind of like

397
00:20:53,750 --> 00:20:54,680
resuming our contract.

398
00:20:54,680 --> 00:20:55,720
A new start.

399
00:20:57,710 --> 00:20:58,680
Really?

400
00:20:59,320 --> 00:21:00,230
You don't want to?

401
00:21:02,480 --> 00:21:03,390
I...

402
00:21:03,960 --> 00:21:04,630
I don't mind

403
00:21:04,630 --> 00:21:05,840
