404
00:21:06,240 --> 00:21:07,390
Well then...

405
00:21:07,670 --> 00:21:08,830
Okay. Let's do that.

406
00:21:09,040 --> 00:21:10,080
I'll pack my stuff

407
00:21:10,080 --> 00:21:11,150
and tell my dad about it.

408
00:21:19,520 --> 00:21:20,800
Newlyweds.

409
00:21:20,910 --> 00:21:22,240
Only us two.

410
00:21:33,670 --> 00:21:34,400
Should I see them off?

411
00:21:36,520 --> 00:21:37,320
Should I not?

412
00:21:38,840 --> 00:21:39,590
I should.

413
00:21:39,880 --> 00:21:41,230
Why can't they stay here?

414
00:21:41,230 --> 00:21:43,350
If you live here, I'll feed you

415
00:21:43,480 --> 00:21:44,630
and you don't have to pay the rent.

416
00:21:45,160 --> 00:21:47,110
Did we bother both of you?

417
00:21:47,790 --> 00:21:48,630
I should not.

418
00:21:51,750 --> 00:21:52,520
I should.

419
00:21:52,520 --> 00:21:53,520
Should not.

420
00:21:54,070 --> 00:21:55,400
It's a good idea for you to go back there.

421
00:21:55,510 --> 00:21:57,230
It's more convenient for you two.

422
00:21:57,230 --> 00:21:57,870
Hurry up.

423
00:21:58,160 --> 00:21:59,710
I'll be waiting for your good news.

424
00:21:59,710 --> 00:22:01,590
Thank you, Aunt Yang. I hope the same, too.

425
00:22:03,800 --> 00:22:04,840
Well...

426
00:22:04,920 --> 00:22:05,680
Where's Mr. Lu?

427
00:22:06,830 --> 00:22:07,560
Where's your dad?

428
00:22:07,840 --> 00:22:08,910
How would I know?

429
00:22:09,720 --> 00:22:10,720
I'll check on him.

430
00:22:11,360 --> 00:22:12,710
Take care.

431
00:22:13,150 --> 00:22:13,520
Okay.

432
00:22:13,520 --> 00:22:14,790
Come back and eat with us sometimes.

433
00:22:16,440 --> 00:22:16,990
Fangning,

434
00:22:17,110 --> 00:22:18,430
remember to come home more often.

435
00:22:20,640 --> 00:22:21,480
Fangning,

436
00:22:21,830 --> 00:22:22,670
take care of yourself.

437
00:22:23,070 --> 00:22:24,000
Don't worry.

438
00:22:24,440 --> 00:22:25,350
I had been living alone

439
00:22:25,350 --> 00:22:26,590
over the years.

440
00:22:28,750 --> 00:22:30,040
And now she has me.

441
00:22:30,280 --> 00:22:31,800
I'll take good care of Fangning.

442
00:23:00,320 --> 00:23:01,510
Where's she?

443
00:23:02,270 --> 00:23:03,390
-What?
-Where's she?

444
00:23:04,190 --> 00:23:05,230
Fangning?

445
00:23:05,470 --> 00:23:06,350
She left a while ago.

446
00:23:06,600 --> 00:23:07,550
They left?

447
00:23:09,360 --> 00:23:10,310
What a nice weather.

448
00:23:10,310 --> 00:23:10,910
Aunt Gao,

449
00:23:10,910 --> 00:23:12,430
please get the quilts to air them out.

450
00:23:12,430 --> 00:23:13,360
Wait, wait.

451
00:23:13,360 --> 00:23:13,800
Wait.

452
00:23:15,000 --> 00:23:16,550
Am I that unreasonable?

453
00:23:19,070 --> 00:23:20,550
No, no.

454
00:23:25,160 --> 00:23:27,040
The old saying is right.

455
00:23:27,640 --> 00:23:29,560
A grown girl can't be kept at home.

456
00:23:29,560 --> 00:23:31,350
If you insist on keeping her,

457
00:23:31,880 --> 00:23:33,230
she'll come to hate you.

458
00:23:42,560 --> 00:23:43,710
That's right.

459
00:23:54,190 --> 00:23:56,200
Go in. What are you thinking about?

460
00:23:56,200 --> 00:23:57,750
"The CEO and Her Doctor."

461
00:23:58,030 --> 00:23:59,430
A sweet holiday.

462
00:24:04,670 --> 00:24:05,990
It's just a book title.

463
00:24:06,590 --> 00:24:08,070
My recent hobby.

464
00:24:27,480 --> 00:24:28,270
It was an unintentional situation

465
00:24:28,270 --> 00:24:29,670
the last few times

466
00:24:29,670 --> 00:24:30,750
you came to my house.

467
00:24:30,750 --> 00:24:31,680
My house is usually

468
00:24:31,680 --> 00:24:32,920
this clean and tidy.

469
00:24:33,630 --> 00:24:35,080
I cleaned it the day before yesterday.

470
00:24:37,360 --> 00:24:38,310
Really?

471
00:24:38,310 --> 00:24:39,920
When you came the day before yesterday,

472
00:24:39,920 --> 00:24:41,400
don't you think that

473
00:24:41,630 --> 00:24:43,000
there was not much cleaning to be done?

474
00:24:43,000 --> 00:24:44,430
It was pretty much the same as now, right?

475
00:24:45,430 --> 00:24:46,840
I'll put the luggage away.

476
00:24:52,590 --> 00:24:53,800
What are you doing?

477
00:24:54,270 --> 00:24:56,110
Are you really sleeping in the guest room?

478
00:24:57,670 --> 00:24:58,560
Where else then?

479
00:24:59,270 --> 00:25:00,190
No.

480
00:25:00,310 --> 00:25:01,560
If we have guests

481
00:25:01,560 --> 00:25:02,560
visiting our home,

482
00:25:02,600 --> 00:25:03,750
they'll find out.

483
00:25:04,680 --> 00:25:05,960
Do you have many guests?

484
00:25:07,240 --> 00:25:09,190
Not that many.

485
00:25:09,190 --> 00:25:11,070
If we do have guests coming over,

486
00:25:11,270 --> 00:25:12,590
we can just tidy up the place.

487
00:25:13,390 --> 00:25:14,360
My work schedule

488
00:25:14,630 --> 00:25:16,400
is different from your schedule.

489
00:25:16,400 --> 00:25:17,630
We shouldn't disturb each other

490
00:25:18,360 --> 00:25:20,070
so that you can sleep better.

491
00:25:20,270 --> 00:25:21,750
I'd like to be disturbed by you.

492
00:25:25,680 --> 00:25:26,920
What are you doing?

493
00:25:27,710 --> 00:25:28,670
I'm putting my luggage in.

494
00:25:29,790 --> 00:25:30,480
You...

495
00:25:30,960 --> 00:25:32,030
Put it somewhere else.

496
00:25:34,630 --> 00:25:35,560
Why?

497
00:25:37,550 --> 00:25:38,430
No reason.

498
00:25:45,400 --> 00:25:46,920
Is there anything in here?

499
00:25:48,120 --> 00:25:49,350
Nothing.

500
00:25:49,350 --> 00:25:50,640
Why can't I put it in?

501
00:25:53,910 --> 00:25:55,960
You can't keep stopping me.

502
00:25:55,960 --> 00:25:57,310
Where else can I put it?

503
00:25:58,150 --> 00:25:58,790
You...

504
00:25:59,190 --> 00:26:00,320
Do you really want to open it?

505
00:26:00,360 --> 00:26:00,960
Yes.

506
00:26:01,000 --> 00:26:01,800
Are you sure?

507
00:26:03,880 --> 00:26:04,520
Okay.

508
00:26:04,520 --> 00:26:06,040
Open it if you want.

509
00:26:06,240 --> 00:26:07,720
I've warned you.

510
00:26:20,680 --> 00:26:22,510
You insisted.

511
00:26:38,560 --> 00:26:40,440
He looks so good even when he folds clothes.

512
00:26:40,640 --> 00:26:42,560
It's okay for us to sleep in separate rooms.

513
00:26:42,560 --> 00:26:43,950
We're married.

514
00:26:43,950 --> 00:26:45,120
It's just a matter of time.

515
00:26:47,710 --> 00:26:48,680
Are you done?

516
00:26:51,070 --> 00:26:52,000
Let's do some grocery shopping

517
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:53,150
