518
00:26:53,990 --> 00:26:54,920
It's because...

519
00:26:55,910 --> 00:26:56,680
It had always been just me

520
00:26:57,040 --> 00:26:58,830
in this house.

521
00:26:58,830 --> 00:26:59,960
So I only prepared the daily necessities

522
00:26:59,960 --> 00:27:00,950
for myself.

523
00:27:02,760 --> 00:27:04,200
This is kind of like our new home.

524
00:27:04,200 --> 00:27:06,080
Why don't we replace them with new ones?

525
00:27:07,800 --> 00:27:08,670
Fangning,

526
00:27:09,710 --> 00:27:11,120
I have something to tell you.

527
00:27:12,710 --> 00:27:13,590
What's the matter?

528
00:27:14,320 --> 00:27:16,430
From now on, the living expenses,

529
00:27:16,430 --> 00:27:17,440
management fees,

530
00:27:17,440 --> 00:27:18,520
utility bills,

531
00:27:18,520 --> 00:27:19,760
and the cost of hiring a helper...

532
00:27:21,240 --> 00:27:22,440
This house is mine.

533
00:27:22,440 --> 00:27:23,960
You don't have to worry about that.

534
00:27:26,110 --> 00:27:27,030
Didn't you say

535
00:27:27,030 --> 00:27:28,190
it's our new home?

536
00:27:28,710 --> 00:27:30,510
Although our marriage is a contract,

537
00:27:30,920 --> 00:27:32,670
the marriage certificate is real.

538
00:27:32,910 --> 00:27:34,750
And we're living together.

539
00:27:35,790 --> 00:27:37,750
Even housemates who live together

540
00:27:37,800 --> 00:27:39,390
share the expenses as well.

541
00:27:40,190 --> 00:27:41,160
Not to mention that

542
00:27:41,160 --> 00:27:42,040
I need to carry out my responsibility

543
00:27:42,270 --> 00:27:43,680
as a good husband.

544
00:27:44,590 --> 00:27:46,000
So in the future,

545
00:27:47,040 --> 00:27:48,430
I'll pay these expenses on time every month.

546
00:27:49,910 --> 00:27:51,040
I can't believe

547
00:27:51,040 --> 00:27:52,430
I'm being financially supported.

548
00:27:57,430 --> 00:27:58,160
Thank you.

549
00:28:06,510 --> 00:28:08,080
I know that it sounds like

550
00:28:08,790 --> 00:28:09,990
I'm overestimating myself,

551
00:28:10,470 --> 00:28:11,400
you don't lack money.

552
00:28:11,640 --> 00:28:12,440
What's wrong with that?

553
00:28:12,880 --> 00:28:14,030
Someone wants to support me.

554
00:28:14,030 --> 00:28:14,960
That's great.

555
00:28:15,400 --> 00:28:17,080
Besides, you're my husband.

556
00:28:17,480 --> 00:28:18,160
Enough,

557
00:28:18,600 --> 00:28:19,070
