558
00:28:19,400 --> 00:28:20,240
Let's go out.

559
00:28:20,950 --> 00:28:21,680
There's one more thing.

560
00:28:24,510 --> 00:28:25,680
I'll go on a business trip tomorrow.

561
00:28:26,030 --> 00:28:26,720
Business trip?

562
00:28:31,630 --> 00:28:32,310
Where are you going?

563
00:28:32,600 --> 00:28:33,040
I mean...

564
00:28:33,040 --> 00:28:34,150
You just got married.

565
00:28:34,150 --> 00:28:35,200
