566
00:28:39,380 --> 00:28:39,830
Okay...

567
00:28:40,400 --> 00:28:41,080
A business trip.

568
00:28:42,150 --> 00:28:43,360
It's your job.

569
00:28:43,830 --> 00:28:44,950
I can understand that.

570
00:28:45,070 --> 00:28:46,720
I can take care of myself.

571
00:28:47,190 --> 00:28:48,070
For how long?

572
00:28:48,070 --> 00:28:48,950
Just a short trip.

573
00:28:49,070 --> 00:28:49,840
Just three days.

574
00:28:49,840 --> 00:28:50,680
Three days?

575
00:28:52,310 --> 00:28:53,510
Three days is fine.

576
00:28:54,240 --> 00:28:55,280
Just three days.

577
00:28:57,200 --> 00:28:57,640
You may go.

578
00:28:59,430 --> 00:29:00,470
[After three days,]

579
00:29:00,830 --> 00:29:02,480
[you'll be mine.]

580
00:29:15,320 --> 00:29:16,720
You could have just left.

581
00:29:17,510 --> 00:29:18,040
Why bother

582
00:29:18,040 --> 00:29:19,680
