586
00:30:00,790 --> 00:30:03,000
Tyrosine can help ease your mood.

587
00:30:04,070 --> 00:30:06,390
Didn't you go to the airport?

588
00:30:06,870 --> 00:30:08,840
When I got to the airport,

589
00:30:09,510 --> 00:30:11,400
I found out that I forgot
to remind you to drink milk

